♪ SINCE YOU CALLED ♪

12:46.542 --> 12:47.917
♪ I'VE BEEN SO CRAZY ♪

12:47.917 --> 12:51.750
♪ I'M JUST ABOUT
TAKING OUR PICTURE ♪

12:51.750 --> 12:53.834
♪ OFF THE WALL ♪

12:53.834 --> 12:57.875
♪ IT'S BEEN 3 MONTHS,
OVER 100 DAYS ♪

12:57.875 --> 12:59.166
♪ SINCE YOU ♪

12:59.166 --> 13:02.542
♪ HELD MY HAND ♪

13:02.542 --> 13:04.750
♪ AND I MISS YOU
